# ─── Autonomy Control Plane (Thin Wrapper / Thick Kernel design) ─────────────
# These directories form the LOCAL-ONLY autonomous execution infrastructure:
#   .github/skills/   — 69 nexus-ai-* SKILL.md agent definitions (not portable code)
#   .github/prompts/  — 34 SOP .prompt.md files (operator-specific, env-specific)
#
# Design intent: The Kernel (nexus-ai-kernel-orchestrator) and all specialist agents
# live here and are intentionally NOT committed. Each deployment environment generates
# its own agent pack. Do NOT remove these gitignore lines.
.github/skills/
.github/prompts/

