# ─── Local Planning Assets (local-only, autonomy planner input) ──────────────
# These directories contain working-environment files used by the autonomy
# engine as planner inputs. They are LOCAL-ONLY:
#   docs/registry/       — Feature registries (v2, v3, sprint seeds). Generated
#                          by scripts/build_operational_registry.py. Regenerate
#                          locally; do not commit generated CSVs/JSOLs.
#   docs/sprint-tickets/ — Sprint board and ticket stubs. Lifecycle-managed by
#                          the autonomy engine. Not portable across deployments.
#   scripts/             — Audit/build helper scripts. Local tooling only.
#
# NOTE: The autonomy planner references specific filenames in these dirs.
# If a referenced file is missing, create a stub locally; do not remove the
# gitignore entries to work around missing stubs.
docs/registry/
docs/sprint-tickets/
scripts/
.nexus/